<subSubSection pageId="29" pageNumber="30" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="29.[151,1436,479,730]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,319,666,692]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was described based on thirteen specimens collected from Chinese 
<collectingCountry box="[1284,1371,666,692]" name="Taiwan" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
from July to August. We have not collected this species to date.
</paragraph>
